<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="description"
              content="sbomify workspace invitation notification">
        <meta name="keywords"
              content="sbomify, workspace, invitation, notification">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>You've been invited to access {{ team.name }}'s Trust Center</title>
        <style>
            .invite-button {
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: white;
                padding: 12px 24px;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 5px;
                display: inline-block;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            .info-box {
                background-color: #f8f9fa;
                border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
                padding: 15px;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>You've been invited to access {{ team.name }}'s Trust Center</h1>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>
            {{ user.get_full_name|default:user.email }} has invited you to access the workspace <strong>{{ team.name }}</strong> on sbomify.
        </p>
        <div class="info-box">
            <p>
                <strong>What happens next?</strong>
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>If you don't have an account, you'll be prompted to create one</li>
                <li>You may be asked to sign a non-disclosure agreement (NDA) if required</li>
                <li>After completing these steps, you'll automatically gain access to gated components and documents</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p>
            <a href="{{ base_url }}{% url 'teams:accept_invite' invitation.token %}"
               class="invite-button">Accept Invitation</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you can't click the button above, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p>{{ base_url }}{% url 'teams:accept_invite' invitation.token %}</p>
        <p>This invitation will expire on {{ invitation.expires_at|date:"F d, Y" }}.</p>
        <p>
            Best regards,
            <br>
            The sbomify Team
        </p>
    </body>
</html>
